<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<LanguageData>
  
  <!-- EN: Mechanoid ship destroyed -->
  <VFEM_MechShipDestroyed.label>机械体飞船被毁</VFEM_MechShipDestroyed.label>
  <!-- EN: {FACTION_name} destroyed {1} -->
  <VFEM_MechShipDestroyed.letterLabel>{FACTION_name}摧毁了{1}</VFEM_MechShipDestroyed.letterLabel>
  <!-- EN: Through clever strategies, large number of casualties and incredible perseverance, {FACTION_name} managed to destroy {1}. -->
  <VFEM_MechShipDestroyed.letterText>在经历了艰苦卓绝的作战，并承受了大量牺牲后，{FACTION_name}成功摧毁了{1}。</VFEM_MechShipDestroyed.letterText>
  
  <!-- EN: ship landing carrier -->
  <VFEM_ShipLandCarrier.label>飞船着陆：航天母舰</VFEM_ShipLandCarrier.label>
  <!-- EN: Ship Landed: Carrier -->
  <VFEM_ShipLandCarrier.letterLabel>飞船着陆：航天母舰</VFEM_ShipLandCarrier.letterLabel>
  <!-- EN: {0} sent a new ship to land on the planet.\n\nCarrier is the biggest ship in the mechanoid hive, heavily defended and with numerous means of producing new, combat-ready mechanoid units. When destroyed, mechanoid presence on the surface will be lowered.\n\nIf it's left operational, it will contribute to the size of mechanoid attack parties. -->
  <VFEM_ShipLandCarrier.letterText>{0}派遣了一艘新战舰着陆与这颗星球之上。\n\n航母是机巢最大的战舰，防御火力强大，同时能生产各式战斗机械体。摧毁它可以降低这颗星球上的机械体活跃程度。\n\n如果不摧毁，它会持续补给机械体的攻击军队。</VFEM_ShipLandCarrier.letterText>
  
  <!-- EN: ship landing cruiser -->
  <VFEM_ShipLandCruiser.label>飞船着陆：巡洋舰</VFEM_ShipLandCruiser.label>
  <!-- EN: Ship Landed: Cruiser -->
  <VFEM_ShipLandCruiser.letterLabel>飞船着陆：巡洋舰</VFEM_ShipLandCruiser.letterLabel>
  <!-- EN: {0} sent a new ship to land on the planet.\n\nCruiser is a medium-sized ship usually serving as a bulk of a mechanoid hive fleet. Is has a number of short range defensive measures, but lacks long range weaponry. When destroyed, mechanoid presence on the surface will be lowered.\n\nIf it's left operational, it will contribute to the size of mechanoid attack parties. -->
  <VFEM_ShipLandCruiser.letterText>{0}派遣了一艘新战舰着陆与这颗星球之上。\n\n这是一艘中等尺寸的巡洋舰，是机巢舰队的中坚力量。它有不少近程火力却缺乏远程武器。摧毁它可以降低这颗星球上的机械体活跃程度。\n\n如果不摧毁，它会持续补给机械体的攻击军队。</VFEM_ShipLandCruiser.letterText>
  
  <!-- EN: ship landing destroyer -->
  <VFEM_ShipLandDestroyer.label>飞船着陆：驱逐舰</VFEM_ShipLandDestroyer.label>
  <!-- EN: Ship Landed: Destroyer -->
  <VFEM_ShipLandDestroyer.letterLabel>飞船着陆：驱逐舰</VFEM_ShipLandDestroyer.letterLabel>
  <!-- EN: {0} sent a new ship to land on the planet.\n\nDestroyer is a medium-sized ship usually serving as mechanoid hive defender. It has no short range defenses. When destroyed, mechanoid presence on the surface will be lowered.\n\nIf it's left operational, it will contribute to the size of mechanoid attack parties. -->
  <VFEM_ShipLandDestroyer.letterText>{0}派遣了一艘新战舰着陆与这颗星球之上。\n\n这是一艘中等尺寸的驱逐舰，常用于护卫机巢。它缺乏近距离自卫火力。摧毁它可以降低这颗星球上的机械体活跃程度。\n\n如果不摧毁，它会持续补给机械体的攻击军队。</VFEM_ShipLandDestroyer.letterText>
  
  <!-- EN: ship landing frigate -->
  <VFEM_ShipLandFrigate.label>飞船着陆：护卫舰</VFEM_ShipLandFrigate.label>
  <!-- EN: Ship Landed: Frigate -->
  <VFEM_ShipLandFrigate.letterLabel>飞船着陆：护卫舰</VFEM_ShipLandFrigate.letterLabel>
  <!-- EN: {0} sent a new ship to land on the planet.\n\nA small ship often used for ground recon operations. It has minimal defenses. When destroyed, mechanoid presence on the surface will be lowered.\n\nIf it's left operational, it will contribute to the size of mechanoid attack parties. -->
  <VFEM_ShipLandFrigate.letterText>{0}派遣了一艘新战舰着陆与这颗星球之上。\n\n这是一艘用于侦察或护卫用的小船。自卫能力薄弱。摧毁它可以降低这颗星球上的机械体活跃程度。\n\n如果不摧毁，它会持续补给机械体的攻击军队。</VFEM_ShipLandFrigate.letterText>
  
  <!-- EN: ship landing troopship -->
  <VFEM_ShipLandTroopship.label>飞船着陆：登陆舰</VFEM_ShipLandTroopship.label>
  <!-- EN: Ship Landed: Troopship -->
  <VFEM_ShipLandTroopship.letterLabel>飞船着陆：登陆舰</VFEM_ShipLandTroopship.letterLabel>
  <!-- EN: {0} sent a new ship to land on the planet.\n\nTroopship is a large mechanoid factory-ship, capable of producing large amounts of combat-ready mechanoids in very little time. When destroyed, mechanoid presence on the surface will be lowered.\n\nIf it's left operational, it will contribute to the size of mechanoid attack parties. -->
  <VFEM_ShipLandTroopship.letterText>{0}派遣了一艘新战舰着陆与这颗星球之上。\n\n这是一艘搭载了机械体工厂的飞船，可以迅速生产出大量战斗机械体。摧毁它可以降低这颗星球上的机械体活跃程度。\n\n如果不摧毁，它会持续补给机械体的攻击军队。</VFEM_ShipLandTroopship.letterText>
  
</LanguageData>